Description: Collective Context Commander - Core Package
 The Collective Context Commander (CCC) is a multi-agent AI orchestration
 tool that solves the "Groundhog Day" problem of AI sessions by providing
 persistent context management across multiple AI agents.
 .
 This package provides the core ccc command-line tool.

